---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Developer & creative builder focused on automation, local-first apps, and AI.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[65ch] px-6 py-20">
    <div class="border border-terracotta/30 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About Tarlow</h1>
      <div class="mt-4 h-0.5 w-12 rounded bg-terracotta"></div>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-[1.0625rem] leading-relaxed text-ink/80">
        <p>Hello, I'm Tarlow.</p>
          <p>
            I have always been a tinkerer and explorer. Since I was young I always had a fascination with building gadgets and tools, diving deep into learning, and finding ways to put my own creative touch on whatever was in front of me.
          </p>
          <p>
            These days, I am doing much of the same but now I get to help other people's ideas and dreams become a reality.
          </p>
        <p>
            I’m a developer focused on bridging the gap between great business ideas and automated solutions. Too often, companies have powerful processes that get hampered by clunky technology, slow websites, or manual workflow gaps.
          </p>
          <p>
            My job is to fix those disconnects. I specialize in building custom tailored systems, from designing creative user experiences to automating your backend operations with smart AI logic and custom developed apps. I thrive on taking complexity and making it look effortless for you. If you have a big idea that needs structure or automation, let's talk.
          </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 border border-terracotta/30 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Let's Connect</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[1.0625rem] text-ink/70">
        Interested in working together or just want to chat about automation and AI?
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="mailto:tarlowspace@proton.me"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-terracotta text-paper font-serif text-lg no-underline hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          Send me an Email
        </a>
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-terracotta/30 text-ink/40 font-serif text-lg cursor-default"
        >
          Discord (coming soon)
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
